<br>
The Cleric mez (Heavenly Visions) is an insta-cast, point-blank AE mez. It has the same duration as the Sorcerer mez, but is also on a timer that is longer than the duration. Thus, the cleric can mez several adds, but they'll be free before he's able to renew the mez on them. It's extremely effective when you're using a main tank who is able to immediately draw agro from all the mobs... a Paladin using the Refresh chant, for example. The cleric can step close to the Paladin, mez the adds, then step back and heal or cast while the group assists on the Paladin. If timed correctly, when the mez wears off the mobs will attack the Paladin again, not go after the cleric that mezed them. Several seconds later, the cleric's mez timer will finish and if needed he can try to re-mez. The mez uses no, or at least virtually no, power to cast.<br>
<br>
Dog<br>
